        "product_description": {
            "value": "Keep your GORE-TEX outerwear looking and performing like new with the GEAR AID Outerwear Care Kit. This complete care system includes Revivex Pro Cleaner and Revivex Wash-In Water Repellent to clean, restore breathability, and protect your gear from water, dirt, and stains. The unscented, low-odor formula is safe for synthetic fabrics and easy to use, making it ideal for backpacking and outdoor adventures. Simply wash your outerwear with the Pro Cleaner, then apply the Wash-In Water Repellent to renew durable water repellency and revive breathable performance. This 20 fl oz kit (Pack of 1) provides everything you need to maintain the quality and longevity of your favorite outerwear.",
